                  City city,

        Constructor of RuralHouse.

        The ReviewState of the rural house will be AWAITING as default until a review is made by an administrator

        Parameters:
        owner - the owner of the rural house
        name - the name of that is given to the rural house
        description - a short text that describes the rural house
        city - the city where the rural house is located
        address - the address where the rural house is
        See Also:
        Review.ReviewState
